    <item>
      <title>A little journal without any ambition</title>
      <link>https://riccardomarin.github.io/posts/first_entry/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Dec 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://riccardomarin.github.io/posts/first_entry/</guid>
      <description>I repent for not keeping a journal during my PhD. Annotating facts and thoughts is essential when dealing with complex processes. I do that for my research projects, but I do not for my academic experience. Curiously, I am also used to writing short tales but never related to my study path. I feel the urge to fill this gap.
Apart from the sentimental perspective (I enjoy reading notes I took years before), this regret has practical reasons.</description>
    </item>
    
